data.revised_prompt: Generate a landscape image that captures an alien military force, reminiscent of futuristic paladins, poised in readiness with advanced weaponry. These are to maintain order in a bizarre, alien landscape. The artistic style should resonate with expansive use of color, a heightened sense of atmospheric perspective, and a touch of surrealism, which is evocative of the artistic era around the turn of the 19th Century. The primary medium should hint at oil painting techniques.
